    "Overall architectureBased on the above design philosophy, the overall architecture of EduStudio is illustrated in Fig. 4.",
    "Steps 2-5 are four templatized modules, while Steps 1 and 6 are common modules that are shared by all the models.",
    "For the four templatized modules (i.e., data preparation, model implementation, training control, and model evaluation), we abstract the intricate elements within each module into various reusable templates.",
    "Within each templatized module, we implement multiple templates with inheritance relationships.",
    "Each template inherits from a basic template prefixed with BaseBase."
